\#AND\#           \#DIVU\#          \#FMUL\#          \#MOVE to USP\#   \#ROL\#
\#ANDI\#          \#DIVUL\#         \#FNEG\#          \#MOVEC\#         \#ROR\#
\#ANDI to CCR\#   \#EOR\#           \#FNOP\#          \#MOVEM\#         \#ROXL\#
\#ANDI to SR\#    \#EORI\#          \#FREM\#          \#MOVEP\#         \#ROXR\#
\#ASL\#           \#EORI to CCR\#   \#FRESTORE\#      \#MOVEQ\#         \#RTD\#
