\#BFCLR\#         \#FACOS\#         \#FSIN\#          \#NBCD\#          \#Scc\#
\#BFEXTS\#        \#FADD\#          \#FSINCOS\#       \#NEG\#           \#STOP\#
\#BFEXTU\#        \#FASIN\#         \#FSINH\#         \#NEGX\#          \#SUB\#
\#BFFFO\#         \#FATAN\#         \#FSQRT\#         \#NOP\#           \#SUBA\#
\#BFINS\#         \#FATANH\#        \#FSUB\#          \#NOT\#           \#SUBI\#
\#BFSET\#         \#FBcc\#          \#FTAN\#          \#OR\#            \#SUBQ\#
\#BFTST\#         \#FCMP\#          \#FTANH\#         \#ORI\#           \#SUBX\#
\#BKPT\#          \#FCOS\#          \#FTENTOX\#       \#ORI to CCR\#    \#SWAP\#
