screen( "ST Functional" )
List of 68000 assembly language instructions in functional groups.
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Transfer     \#MOVE\# \#MOVEA\# \#MOVEM\# \#MOVEP\# \#MOVEQ\# \#CLR\#
Registers    \#EXG\# \#EXT\# \#SWAP\#
Address      \#LEA\# \#PEA\#
BCD          \#ABCD\# \#SBCD\# \#NBCD\#
Add          \#ADD\# \#ADDA\# \#ADDI\# \#ADDQ\# \#ADDX\#
Subtract     \#SUB\# \#SUBA\# \#SUBI\# \#SUBQ\# \#SUBX\# 
Negate       \#NEG\# \#NEGX\#
Multiply     \#MULS\# \#MULU\#
Divide       \#DIVS\# \#DIVU\#
Shift        \#ASL\# \#ASR\# \#LSL\# \#LSR\#
Rotate       \#ROL\# \#ROR\# \#ROXL\# \#ROXR\#
Bit Flags    \#BCHG\# \#BCLR\# \#BSET\# \#BTST\#
Logical      \#AND\# \#ANDI\# \#OR\# \#ORI\# \#EOR\# \#EORI\# \#NOT\#
\#CCR\#          \#ANDI to CCR\# \#ORI to CCR\# \#EORI to CCR\# \#MOVE from SR\#
Test         \#TST\# \#TAS\#
Compare      \#CMP\# \#CMPA\# \#CMPI\# \#CMPM\# \#CMP2\#
Branch       \#Bcc\# \#DBcc\# \#Scc\#  (substitute \#Condition Codes\# for 'cc')
Jump         \#BRA\# \#BSR\# \#DBRA\# \#JMP\# \#JSR\#
Return       \#RTS\# \#RTR\#
Stack Frame  \#LINK\# \#UNLK\#
\#Exceptions\#   \#CHK\# \#ILLEGAL\# \#TRAP\# \#TRAPV\#
No Operation \#NOP\#
\end

