\#SR\#           \#MOVE to SR\# \#ANDI to SR\# \#ORI to SR\# \#EORI to SR\#
\#USP\#          \#MOVE from USP\# \#MOVE to USP\#
I/O          \#RESET\# \#STOP\#
\end

screen( "TT Functional" )
List of 68030 assembly language instructions in functional groups.
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Transfer     \#MOVE\# \#MOVEA\# \#MOVEM\# \#MOVEP\# \#MOVEQ\# \#CLR\#
Registers    \#EXG\# \#EXT\# \#EXTB\# \#SWAP\#
Address      \#LEA\# \#PEA\#
BCD          \#ABCD\# \#SBCD\# \#NBCD\# \#PACK\# \#UNPK\#
Add          \#ADD\# \#ADDA\# \#ADDI\# \#ADDQ\# \#ADDX\#
Subtract     \#SUB\# \#SUBA\# \#SUBI\# \#SUBQ\# \#SUBX\# 
Negate       \#NEG\# \#NEGX\#
Multiply     \#MULS\# \#MULU\# \#MULS.L\# \#MULU.L\#
Divide       \#DIVS\# \#DIVU\# \#DIVSL\# \#DIVUL\#
Shift        \#ASL\# \#ASR\# \#LSL\# \#LSR\#
Rotate       \#ROL\# \#ROR\# \#ROXL\# \#ROXR\#
Bit Flags    \#BCHG\# \#BCLR\# \#BSET\# \#BTST\#
Bit Fields   \#BFCLR\# \#BFEXTS\# \#BFEXTU\# \#BFFFO\# \#BFINS\# \#BFSET\# \#BFTST\#
Logical      \#AND\# \#ANDI\# \#OR\# \#ORI\# \#EOR\# \#EORI\# \#NOT\#
\#CCR\#          \#MOVE from CCR\# \#MOVE to CCR\#
             \#ANDI to CCR\# \#ORI to CCR\# \#EORI to CCR\#
Test         \#TST\# \#TAS\#
Compare      \#CMP\# \#CMPA\# \#CMPI\# \#CMPM\# \#CMP2\# \#CAS\# \#CAS2\#
