Time charts: \#LEA.L\#

<ea>: \#(An)\# \#d(An)\# \#d(An,Rx)\# \#d(PC)\# \#d(PC,Rx)\#
      \#addr\# \#([b,An],Rx,d)\# \#([b,An,Rx],d)\# \#([b,PC],Rx,d)\# \#([b,PC,Rx],d)\#


