\#Flags:\# N=* Z=* V=0 C=0

Time charts: \#MOVE.W\#, \#MOVE.L\#

Source <ea>: \#Dn\# \#An\# \#(An)\# \#(An)+\# \#-(An)\# \#d(An)\# \#d(An,Rx)\# \#d(PC)\# \#d(PC,Rx)\#
             \#addr\# \##data\# \#([b,An],Rx,d)\# \#([b,An,Rx],d)\# \#([b,PC],Rx,d)\# \#([b,PC,Rx],d)\#

Dest <ea>: \#Dn\# \#(An)\# \#(An)+\# \#-(An)\# \#d(An)\# \#d(An,Rx)\#
           \#addr\# \#([b,An],Rx,d)\# \#([b,An,Rx],d)\#


MOVE <ea>,An     translated as  MOVEA <ea>,An
MOVE.L #data,Dn  translated as  MOVEQ #data,Dn  for -128 to 127

See also: \#MOVEA\#, \#MOVEC\#, \#MOVEM\#, \#MOVEP\#, \#MOVEQ\#, \#MOVES\#, \#MOVE16\#,
