NEG <ea>

    Negate binary.  <ea> = -<ea>.

\#Sizes:\# Byte, Word, Long

\#CPUs:\# 01234

\#Flags:\# N=* Z=* V=* X=C=*

Time charts: \#NEG.W\#, \#NEG.L\#

<ea>: \#Dn\# \#(An)\# \#(An)+\# \#-(An)\# \#d(An)\# \#d(An,Rx)\#
