\#Flags:\# N=* V=* Z=* X=C=*   (Z either cleared or unchanged)

Time charts: \#NEGX.W\#, \#NEGX.L\#

<ea>: \#Dn\# \#(An)\# \#(An)+\# \#-(An)\# \#d(An)\# \#d(An,Rx)\#
      \#addr\# \#([b,An],Rx,d)\# \#([b,An,Rx],d)\#


See also \#NEG\#
\end

