screen( sensitive("OR") )
OR <ea>,\#Dn\#
OR \#Dn\#,<ea>

    Bitwise or.  \#Dest\# |= \#Source\#.

\#Sizes:\# Byte, Word, Long

\#CPUs:\# 01234

\#Flags:\# N=* Z=* V=0 C=0

Time charts: \#OR.W\#, \#OR.L\#

Source <ea>: \#Dn\# \#An\# \#(An)\# \#(An)+\# \#-(An)\# \#d(An)\# \#d(An,Rx)\# \#d(PC)\# \#d(PC,Rx)\#
             \#addr\# \##data\# \#([b,An],Rx,d)\# \#([b,An,Rx],d)\# \#([b,PC],Rx,d)\# \#([b,PC,Rx],d)\#

Dest <ea>: \#Dn\# \#(An)\# \#(An)+\# \#-(An)\# \#d(An)\# \#d(An,Rx)\#
           \#addr\# \#([b,An],Rx,d)\# \#([b,An,Rx],d)\#


OR #data,<ea>  translated as  ORI #data,<ea>

See also \#AND\#, \#ANDI\#, \#EOR\#, \#EORI\#, \#NOT\#, \#ORI\#
         \#ANDI to CCR\#, \#EORI to CCR\#, \#ORI to CCR\#,
         \#ANDI to SR\#, \#EORI to SR\#, \#ORI to SR\#
\end

