<ea>: \#Dn\# \#An\# \#(An)\# \#(An)+\# \#-(An)\# \#d(An)\# \#d(An,Rx)\# \#d(PC)\# \#d(PC,Rx)\#
      \#addr\# \##data\# \#([b,An],Rx,d)\# \#([b,An,Rx],d)\# \#([b,PC],Rx,d)\# \#([b,PC,Rx],d)\#


See also \#ADD\#, \#ADDA\#, \#ADDI\#, \#ADDX\#, \#SUB\#, \#SUBI\#, \#SUBQ\#, \#SUBX\#
