Time charts: \#SUBI.W\#, \#SUBI.L\#

<ea>: \#Dn\# \#(An)\# \#(An)+\# \#-(An)\# \#d(An)\# \#d(An,Rx)\#
      \#addr\# \#([b,An],Rx,d)\# \#([b,An,Rx],d)\#


