\#Sizes:\# Byte, Word, Long

\#CPUs:\# 01234

\#Flags:\# N=* Z=* V=* X=C=*  (Z either cleared or unchanged)

Time charts: \#SUBX.W\#, \#SUBX.L\#


See also \#ADD\#, \#ADDA\#, \#ADDI\#, \#ADDX\#, \#SUB\#, \#SUBA\#, \#SUBI\#, \#SUBQ\#
         \#NEG\#, \#NEGX\#
