-------+-------+-------+--------+--------+--------+-------+--------+
 12+4m | 12+4m | 16+4m |  18+4m |  16+4m |  20+4m | 16+4m |  18+4m |
-------+-------+-------+--------+--------+--------+-------+--------+

<m> is the number of registers moved.
\end

screen( "MOVEM.L" )
\#MOVEM\#.L             68000 Instruction Timing Charts
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Save Registers to Memory
-------+-------+-------+--------+--------+--------+
  (An) | -(An) | d(An) |d(An,Rx)| addr.W | addr.L |
-------+-------+-------+--------+--------+--------+
  8+8m |  8+8m | 12+8m |  14+8m |  12+8m |  16+8m |
-------+-------+-------+--------+--------+--------+

Restore Registers from Memory
-------+-------+-------+--------+--------+--------+-------+--------+
  (An) | (An)+ | d(An) |d(An,Rx)| addr.W | addr.L | d(PC) |d(PC,Rx)|
-------+-------+-------+--------+--------+--------+-------+--------+
 12+8m | 12+8m | 16+8m |  18+8m |  16+8m |  20+8m | 16+8m |  18+8m |
-------+-------+-------+--------+--------+--------+-------+--------+

<m> is the number of registers moved.
\end

