screen( "MOVE to CCR Time",
		"MOVE to SR Time" )
\#MOVE to SR\# \#MOVE to CCR\#
                       68000 Instruction Timing Chart
----------------------------------------------------------------------
        |    Dest     |
 Source +------+------+
        |  SR  | CCR  |
--------+------+------+
   Dn   |   6  |   6  |
--------+------+------+
  (An)  |  12  |  12  |
  (An)+ |  12  |  12  |
  -(An) |  14  |  14  |
--------+------+------+
  d(An) |  16  |  16  |
d(An,Rx)|  18  |  18  |
--------+------+------+
 addr.W |  16  |  16  |
 addr.L |  20  |  20  |
--------+------+------+
  d(PC) |  16  |  16  |
d(PC,Rx)|  18  |  18  |
--------+------+------+
  #data |  12  |  12  |
--------+------+------+
\end

