    Causes TRAPV exception on \link("PMMU Condition Codes")PMMU Condition Code\#.
    Optional data will be included in exception stack frame.

\#Sizes:\# Word, Long

\#CPUs:\# 5

<ea> = \#Dn\# \#(An)\# \#(An)+\# \#-(An)\# \#d(An)\# \#d(An,Rx)\# \#([b,An],Rx,d)\# \#([b,An,Rx],d)\#
       \#addr\#
\end

