Addressing mode for MC68020 only
----------------------------------------------------------------------
\#([b,An],Rx,d)\#, \#([b,An,Rx],d)\#, \#([b,PC],Rx,d)\# and \#([b,PC,Rx],d)\#
addressing modes were implemented on \#CPUs:\# 234 only.

\#d(An,Rx)\# and \#d(PC,Rx)\# addressing modes cannot use the size modifier
(Rx = D0.W) for \#CPUs:\# 01.

Also, 32 bit PC relative was not implemented until \#CPUs:\# 234.

